text: Supreme is an American clothes and skateboarding store made in New York City in April 1994. The company is focused with street wear, skateboarding, and hip hop ideas. Supreme makes skateboards and clothing. It was bought by VF Corporation in December 2020 for $2.1 billion. == Awards == In 2018, Supreme was given the Council of Fashion Designers of America's Menswear Designer of the Year Award. == References == Category:American clothing companies
